Hi.

1:19:31.880 --> 1:19:33.560
Hi.

1:19:34.480 --> 1:19:36.360
Hey. Hi.

1:19:38.080 --> 1:19:41.120
Oh, thank you. Thank you.
Ah, thank you, sir.

1:19:42.560 --> 1:19:45.000
I'll have grandchildren!

1:19:46.120 --> 1:19:48.560
Liking the Dalmatian
look on Mrs. P.

1:19:48.680 --> 1:19:50.560
Oh, yes.
That is a tail-wagger.

1:19:51.320 --> 1:19:54.400
Uh, is she going
on the honeymoon too?

1:19:55.080 --> 1:19:58.040
Bye, everyone!
Bye! Thank you!

1:19:58.120 --> 1:20:01.920
Bye! Goodbye! Thank you!

