Hey, Gabe. I'm sorry that Diane
aired the story before you did.

1:20:08.160 --> 1:20:11.000
Yeah, it's okay.
I got a call into Geraldo.

1:20:11.120 --> 1:20:12.960
So, tell me,
what's your whole secret?

1:20:13.040 --> 1:20:14.200
What?

1:20:14.280 --> 1:20:17.080
Come on. You always
get the inside story.

1:20:17.160 --> 1:20:18.760
Oh, Gabe.

1:20:18.880 --> 1:20:21.200
Okay. There is no secret.

1:20:21.280 --> 1:20:23.480
It's all about skill.

1:20:23.560 --> 1:20:25.120
Oh, hey, Jack.

1:20:25.760 --> 1:20:29.000
I heard that you got your scholarship
renewed. Congratulations.

1:20:29.080 --> 1:20:31.000
-Hey, Jen!
-Hey.

1:20:31.080 --> 1:20:34.960
Thank you. I'm looking forward
to going back to Millington.

1:20:35.880 --> 1:20:38.000
Partly because of you.

1:20:38.080 --> 1:20:40.000
Well, you didn't have to say that,

1:20:40.080 --> 1:20:41.800
