Lexy, on the case.

1:20:48.800 --> 1:20:51.560
You should be
proud of yourself.

1:20:51.640 --> 1:20:54.760
I learned something totally
important from you, Jack.

1:20:54.840 --> 1:20:56.960
Things aren't always
what they appear to be.

1:20:57.040 --> 1:21:00.200
And that's good.
It keeps life interesting.

