Are you starting a new
paper handbag trend?

1:21:05.760 --> 1:21:08.160
Get a clue, Jack.
I've been shopping.

1:21:08.240 --> 1:21:10.080
Of course.

1:21:10.160 --> 1:21:11.920
It's for you.

1:21:17.600 --> 1:21:21.360
I found them at a vintage shop,
and I sort of customized them.

1:21:22.880 --> 1:21:25.280
Thank you. I like 'em.

