the shoes that other people have worn?

1:21:37.560 --> 1:21:39.640
Shoes. Eww!

1:21:39.720 --> 1:21:42.400
I think I can survive
wearing pre-worn shoes, guys.

1:21:42.480 --> 1:21:45.080
Lexy, are you crazy?

1:21:45.160 --> 1:21:47.280
You don't know where
those shoes have been.

1:21:47.360 --> 1:21:49.920
Does the word "fungi"
mean anything to you?

1:21:50.000 --> 1:21:53.280
Come on, Jen. My feet aren't
that elite. Neither are yours.

1:21:53.360 --> 1:21:54.920
Get with the planet.

